 it, he finds that it was nothing: instead, he finds [that] God [has always been present] with him, and [that] He will pay him his account in full - for God is swift in reckoning!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2830.mp3","surahId":24,"words":[{"id":40676,"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"আর যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/024_039_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40677,"position":2,"arabic":"كَفَرُوٓا۟","translation":"অস্বীকার করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_039_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40678,"position":3,"arabic":"أَعْمَـٰلُهُمْ","translation":"তাদের কর্মসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/024_039_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40679,"position":4,"arabic":"كَسَرَابٍۭ","translation":"মতো মরীচিকার","audioUrl":"wbw/024_039_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40680,"position":5,"arabic":"بِقِيعَةٍۢ","translation":"মধ্যে মরুভূমির","audioUrl":"wbw/024_039_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40681,"position":6,"arabic":"يَحْسَبُهُ","translation":"তাকে মনে করে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_039_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40682,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلظَّمْـَٔانُ","translation":"পিপাসার্ত লোক","audioUrl":"wbw/024_039_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40683,"position":8,"arabic":"مَآءً","translation":"পানি (হিসেবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_039_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40684,"position":9,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰٓ","translation":"এমনকি","audioUrl":"wbw/024_039_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40685,"position":10,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/024_039_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40686,"position":11,"arabic":"جَآءَهُۥ","translation":"সেখানে পৌঁছলো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_039_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40687,"position":12,"arabic":"لَمْ","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/024_039_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40688,"position":13,"arabic":"يَجِدْهُ","translation":"সেখানে পেলো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_039_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40689,"position":14,"arabic":"شَ