","audioUrl":"wbw/024_040_035.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41537,"position":34,"arabic":"٤٠","translation":"(৪০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":41,"arabic":"أَلَمْ تَرَ أَنَّ ٱللَّهَ يُسَبِّحُ لَهُۥ مَن فِى ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ وَٱلطَّيْرُ صَٰٓفَّٰتٍۢ ۖ كُلٌّۭ قَدْ عَلِمَ صَلَاتَهُۥ وَتَسْبِيحَهُۥ ۗ وَٱللَّهُ عَلِيمٌۢ بِمَا يَفْعَلُونَ","translation":"ART THOU NOT aware that it is God whose limit­less glory all [creatures] that are in the heavens and on earth extol, even the birds as they spread out their wings? Each [of them] knows indeed how to pray unto Him and to glorify Him; and God has full knowledge of all that they do:","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2832.mp3","surahId":24,"words":[{"id":42288,"position":1,"arabic":"أَلَمْ","translation":"কি নি দেখো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42289,"position":2,"arabic":"تَرَ","translation":"তুমি","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42290,"position":3,"arabic":"أَنَّ","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42291,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌র","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42292,"position":5,"arabic":"يُسَبِّحُ","translation":"পবিত্র মহিমা ঘোষনা করছে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42293,"position":6,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","translation":"জন্যে তাঁরই","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42294,"position":7,"arabic":"مَن","translation":"যা কিছু","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42295,"position":8,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে (অাছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42296,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","translation":"আকাশমণ্ডলির","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42297,"position":10,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"ও পৃথিবীতে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42298,"position":11,"arabic":"وَٱلطَّيْرُ","translation":"আর পাখিরাও (যারা)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42299,"position":12,"arabic":"صَـٰٓفَّـٰتٍۢ ۖ","translation":"ডানা মেলে চলছে (উড়ন্ত)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42301,"position":13,"arabic":"كُلٌّۭ","translation":"প্রত্যেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42302,"position":14,"arabic":"قَدْ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42303,"position":15,"arabic":"عَلِمَ","translation":"জেনে নিয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42304,"position":16,"arabic":"صَلَاتَهُۥ","translation":"তাঁর প্রার্থনার","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42305,"position":17,"arabic":"وَتَسْبِيحَهُۥ ۗ","translation":"ও তাঁর পবিত্র মহিমা ঘোষনা করার (নিয়ম)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42307,"position":18,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"আর আল্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42308,"position":19,"arabic":"عَلِيمٌۢ","translation":"খুব অবহিত","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42309,"position":20,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"ঐ বিষয়ে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42310,"position":21,"arabic":"يَفْعَلُونَ","translation":"তারা করছে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_041_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42311,"position":22,"arabic":"٤١","translation":"(৪১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":42,"arabic":"وَلِلَّهِ مُلْكُ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ ۖ وَإِلَى ٱللَّهِ ٱلْمَصِيرُ","translation":"for, God’s is the dominion over the heavens and the earth, and with God is all journeys’ end.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2833.mp3","surahId":24,"words":[{"id":43072,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلِلَّهِ","translation":"আর জন্যে আল্লাহ্‌রই","audioUrl":"wbw/024_042_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43073,"position":2,"arabic":"مُلْكُ","translation":"সার্বভৌমত্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/024_042_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43074,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","translation":"আকাশমণ্ডলির","audioUrl":"wbw/024_042_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43075,"position":4,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ ۖ","translation":"ও পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/024_042_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43077,"position":5,"arabic":"وَإِلَى","translation":"এবং দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_042_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43078,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌রই","audioUrl":"wbw/024_042_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43079,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْمَصِيرُ","translation":"প্রত্যাবর্তন (সকলেরই)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_042_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43080,"position":8,"arabic":"٤٢","translation":"(৪২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":43,"arabic":"أَلَمْ تَرَ أَنَّ ٱللَّهَ يُزْجِى سَحَابًۭا ثُمَّ يُؤَلِّفُ بَيْنَهُۥ ثُمَّ يَجْعَلُهُۥ رُكَامًۭا فَتَرَى ٱلْوَدْقَ يَخْرُجُ مِنْ خِلَٰلِهِۦ وَيُنَزِّلُ مِنَ ٱلسَّمَآءِ مِن جِبَالٍۢ فِيهَا مِنۢ بَرَدٍۢ فَيُصِيبُ بِهِۦ مَن يَشَآءُ وَيَصْرِفُهُۥ عَن مَّن يَشَآءُ ۖ يَكَادُ سَنَا بَرْقِهِۦ يَذْهَبُ بِٱلْأَبْصَٰرِ","translation":"Art thou not aware that it is God who causes the clouds to move onward, then joins them together, then piles them up in masses, until thou can see rain come forth from their midst? And He it is who sends down from the skies, by degrees, mountainous masses [of clouds] charged with hail, striking therewith whomever He wills and averting it from whomever He wills, [the while] the flash of His lightning well-nigh deprives [men of their] sight!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2834.mp3","surahId":24,"words":[{"id":43819,"position":1,"arabic":"أَلَمْ","translation":"কি নি","audioUrl":"wbw/024_043_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43820,"position":2,"arabic":"تَرَ","transl